snippet.title: Hanapon Princess Official Trailer
snippet.description:
One afternoon, after a trip to an antique store, it turns out that a simple statue is actually a magical being from the land of Hanapon. There, the time has come for one of the four princesses to marry a human and become the new queen. But who’s the better candidate to rule? Meet and talk to all the sisters and decide for yourself!

BUY NOW! https://kavorkaplay.com/
